The paper deals with data-driven decision making and analytics tasks, which are typically associated with the database (cs.DB) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the challenges of handling large volumes of data and the need for efficient query processing, which are relevant to the data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of cloud deployments, which falls under the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. Finally, the paper proposes an adaptive learning mechanism, which is a common theme in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
